data.description: This is a quiet community located just outside Shelton.   Timberlakes has a larger lake where motor boats are allowed and a smaller lake with not motor boats allowed.  There are several parks throughout the community.  There is a also a community saltwater access nearby.
data.whatILove: You will love this beautiful property consisting of 2 tax parcels.  This is a very quiet and pieceful part of of the lake.  There are no motors allowed on the smaller part of the lake but you have the option of using the larger Timberlake or enjoy salt water beach access.
